    "causal_summary": "Four deferred P2 findings remain in the rerank sidecar env/config surface. F17 allows malformed config values to enter the canonical hash. F16 and F40 report env allowlist drift between launcher and in-process sidecar clients. F46 requires a documented config-prefix precedence rule where `SPECKIT_*` and `RERANK_*` can express the same sidecar intent.",
